           !!! Educational Purposes Only !!!



BUILD AND RUN
=============
Clone and compile first.
```sh
git clone https://github.com/Taras-1337/instost.git
cd instost
./build.sh
```
Then run insurgency.
And inject (`sudo` required) while in menu or in game...
``` sh
./inject.sh load
```


MODULES
=======
o  Hud
   - Crosshair
   - HP/AMMO
o  Radar (WIP)
o  NoFlash
o  ESP
   - Nickname
   - Skeleton
     - Change color if visible
   - WeaponName
   - Health
   - Range


